                        <p>
                            This Privacy Policy has been created by CLOUDSITE SOLUTION. (Company No. 003093608-V), the owner and operator of www.cloudsite.com.my in accordance with the Malaysia Personal Data Protection Act 2010 and/or any other applicable laws regulations, guidelines, code of practices, circular may be issued from time to time. This Privacy Policy is to protect and maintain the privacy of the users of www.cloudsite.com via our website (“Website”) and/or mobile device application (“App”). We have provided you with this policy statement to inform you of:
